mixin calculator(arr)
	section.calculator(id="calculator")
			div.wrapper.animated
				div.calculator__wrapper
					h2.calculator__title Калькулятор
					include calculatorDelivery.pug
					div.calculator-info.calculator__margin-top40
						h3.calculator-info__title Информация
						ul.calculator-info__ul
							each item, index in arr
								li.calculator-info__item= item